Former Free State premier and current ANC general-secretary Ace Magashule has handed himself over for arrest. Courtesy of #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Former Free State premier Ace Magashule has handed himself over to the Directorate for Priority Crime on Friday. His arrest is being processed. READ: Ramaphosa shies away from Magashule question Magashule is expected to appear in court on charges of corruption in connection with the Free State asbestos tender corruption while he was premier in the province.